\c 8
\s Mukadzi weShunemi anodzoserwa fuma yake yose namambo
\p
\v 1 Zvino Erisha wakataura kumukadzi uyo mwanakomana wake waaiva araramisa\x + 4.35.\x* achiti: Simuka uende, iwe neimba yako, unova mweni kwaunganova mweni. Nokuti Jehovha wadana nzara; uye ichasvika panyika makore manomwe\x + 4.38. Map. 105.16. Hag. 1.11. Gen.. 41.27. 1 Madz. 17.1. Mab. 11.28.\x*.
\v 2 Zvino mukadzi wakasimuka ndokuita zvichienderana neshoko remunhu waMwari. Zvino wakaenda iye nemhuri yake ndokunova mweni munyika yeVaFirisitia makore manomwe.
\v 3 Zvino zvakaitika pakupera kwemakore manomwe, kuti mukadzi wakadzoka kubva kunyika yeVaFirisitia. Zvino wakabuda kunochema kuna mambo pamusoro peimba yake uye pamusoro pemunda wake.
\v 4 Zvino mambo wakataura naGehazi muranda wemunhu waMwari\x + 4.12.\x* achiti: Ndiudze hako zvinhu zvose zvikuru Erisha zvaakaita.
\v 5 Zvino zvakaitika paairondedzera kuna mambo kuti wakamutsa sei wakafa\x + 8.1.\x*, kuti tarira, mukadzi wemwanakomana waaiva amutsa pakufa wakachema kuna mambo pamusoro peimba yake uye pamusoro pemunda wake. Gehazi ndokuti: Ishe wangu mambo, uyu ndiye mukadzi, uye uyu ndiye mwanakomana wake Erisha waakararamisa.
\v 6 Mambo paakabvunza mukadzi, iye wakamuudza. Naizvozvo mambo wakamumisira umwe mutenwa achiti: Dzosera zvose zvaiva zvake negoho rose remunda kubva pazuva raakabva panyika kusvika ikozvino.
\s Hazaeri anotevera Bheni-Hadhadhi paushe hweSiriya
\p
\v 7 Zvino Erisha wakasvika paDhamasiko\x + 1 Madz. 11.24.\x*; zvino Bheni-Hadhadhi mambo weSiriya waiva achirwara\x + 1 Madz. 20.2.\x*; uye wakaudzwa zvichinzi: Munhu waMwari wasvika pano.
\v 8 Zvino mambo wakati kuna Hazaeri\x + 1 Madz. 19.17.\x*: Tora chipo muruoko rwako, ugoenda unosangana nemunhu waMwari\x + 1 Sam. 9.7.\x*, ugobvunza kuna Jehovha naye, uti: Ndichapora pachirwere ichi here?
\v 9 Naizvozvo Hazaeri wakaenda kunosangana naye, ndokutora chipo muruoko rwake, icho chezvakanakisisa zvose zveDhamasiko, mitoro yemakamera makumi mana, ndokusvika ndokumira pamberi pake, ndokuti: Mwanakomana wenyu Bheni-Hadhadhi mambo weSiriya wandituma kwamuri achiti: Ndichapora here pachirwere ichi\x + 5.13.\x*?
\v 10 Erisha ndokuti kwaari: Enda unoti: Ungapora zvekupora asi Jehovha wandiratidza kuti uchafa zvekufa\x + 8.15.\x*.
\v 11 Zvino waka\add mu\add*nan'anidza\add , \add*waka\add mu\add*nan'anidza kusvika anyara; munhu waMwari ndokuchema\x + 2.17.\x*.
\v 12 Zvino Hazaeri wakati: Nemhaka yei tenzi wangu achichema? Iye ndokuti: Nokuti ndinoziva zvakaipa zvauchaitira vana vaIsraeri; nhare dzavo uchatungidza nemoto, uye majaya avo uchauraya nemunondo\x + 10.32. 12.17. 13.3,7,22. Amo. 1.3.\x*, uchapwanya pwere dzavo\x + Isa. 13.16. Hos. 13.16. Nah. 3.10. Map. 137.9. Hos. 10.14.\x*, uye vakadzi vavo vane mimba uchatumbura\x + 15.16. Hos. 13.16. Amo. 1.13.\x*.
\v 13 Zvino Hazaeri akati: Ko muranda wenyu chinyiko, iyo imbwa, kuti ndiite chinhu ichi chikuru\x + 2 Sam. 3.8.\x*? Erisha akati: Jehovha wakandizivisa kuti iwe uchava mambo pamusoro paSiriya\x + 1 Madz. 19.15.\x*.
\v 14 Zvino wakabva kuna Erisha ndokuuya kuna tenzi wake; iye wakati kwaari: Erisha wati chii kwauri? Iye ndokuti: Wakandiudza \add kuti\add*: Uchapora zvekupora\x + 8.10.\x*.
\v 15 Zvino zvakaitika chifume kuti wakatora nguvo yekufukidza ndokunyika mumvura ndokuwaridza pachiso chake kusvika afa; Hazaeri ndokuva mambo pachinzvimbo chake.
\s Jehoramu naAhaziya madzimambo aJudha
\p
\v 16 Zvino mugore rechishanu raJoramu mwanakomana waAhabhi mambo waIsraeri\x + 1.17.\x*, Jehoshafati ari mambo waJudha, Jehoramu mwanakomana waJehoshafati mambo waJudha wakava mambo\x + 2 Makor. 21.1,3,4.\x*.
\v 17 Waiva nemakore makumi matatu nemaviri paakava mambo. Zvino wakatonga makore masere paJerusarema\x + 2 Makor. 21.5-10.\x*.
\v 18 Zvino wakafamba munzira yemadzimambo aIsraeri, sezvakaita imba yaAhabhi; nokuti mukunda waAhabhi waiva mukadzi wake; zvino wakaita zvakaipa pameso aJehovha\x + 8.26. 9.2.\x*.
\v 19 Asi Jehovha waiva asingadi kuparadza Judha, nekuda kwemuranda wake Dhavhidhi, sekuvimbisa kwake kwaari kuti achapa mwenje kwaari \add ne\add*kuvanakomana vake\x + 2 Makor. 21.7.\x* mazuva ese\x + 2 Sam. 7.12,13. Map. 132.11.\x*.
\p
\v 20 Mumazuva ake Edhomu wakapanduka kubva pasi peruoko rwaJudha, ndoku\add zvi\add*isira mambo pamusoro pavo\x + 3.9. 1 Madz. 22.47.\x*.
\v 21 Zvino Joramu wakayambukira kuZairi nengoro dzose dzaiva naye. Iye wakamuka usiku ndokurova VaEdhomu vaiva vakamukomba, nevakuru vengoro; vanhu ndokutizira kumatende avo\x + 2 Sam. 18.17.\x*.
\v 22 Naizvozvo Edhomu wakapanduka kubva muruoko rwaJudha, kusvika zuva ranhasi. Ipapo Ribhina akapanduka nenguva iyo\x + Josh. 10.29. 2 Makor. 21.10.\x*.
\p
\v 23 Uye dzimwe dzenyaya dzaJoramu, nezvese zvaakaita, hazvina kunyorwa here mubhuku reMakoronike emadzimambo aJudha?
\v 24 Zvino Joramu wakarara nemadzibaba ake, ndokuvigwa kumadzibaba ake muguta raDhavhidhi\x + 2 Makor. 21.20.\x*. Ahaziya mwanakomana wake ndokuva mambo pachinzvimbo chake\x + 2 Makor. 22.1-6.\x*.
\p
\v 25 Negore regumi nemaviri raJoramu mwanakomana waAhabhi mambo waIsraeri, Ahaziya mwanakomana waJehoramu mambo waJudha wakava mambo\x + 9.29.\x*.
\v 26 Ahaziya waiva nemakore makumi maviri nemaviri paakava mambo, zvino wakatonga gore rimwe muJerusarema. Zvino zita ramai vake raiva Atariya, mukunda waOmiri mambo waIsraeri\x + 2 Makor. 22.2.\x*.
\v 27 Zvino wakafamba munzira yeimba yaAhabhi, ndokuita zvakaipa pameso aJehovha, se\add zvakaita\add* imba yaAhabhi; nokuti waiva mukwasha weimba yaAhabhi\x + Gen.. 19.14.\x*.
\p
\v 28 Zvino wakaenda naJoramu mwanakomana waAhabhi kunorwa naHazaeri mambo weSiriya\x + 8.15.\x* paRamoti-Giriyadhi\x + 1 Madz. 22.3.\x*; VaSiriya ndokurova Joramu.
\v 29 Zvino mambo Joramu wakadzokera kunorapiwa\x + 9.15.\x* kuJezireeri kubva pamavanga VaSiriya avakamurova\x + Josh. 17.16.\x* paRama pakurwa kwake naHazaeri mambo weSiriya. Ahaziya mwanakomana waJehoramu mambo waJudha ndokuburukira kunoona Joramu mwanakomana waAhabhi paJezireeri, nokuti wairwara\x + 9.16.\x*.